  <description><![CDATA[<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/sicily" title="Sicily">Sicily</a><span>, the island in the heart of the Mediterranean bursting with cultural treasures, delicious cuisine, architectural gems and dramatic landscapes. This escorted tour will take you on a journey through ancient towns, stunning archaeological sites and to see Europe’s largest volcano, Mount Etna. On this trip you’ll have the opportunity to sample some of Sicily’s finest traditional dishes, in stunning Sicilian settings.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>30</p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
